  "text": "The basic element in (8) is a pairwise difference between any two exemplars belonging to the same class. Alternatively, we can view these basic elements as samples of a new space. The construction of such a space is validated by the property C3 to capture the common 'shape' of the face appearance manifold. This space is called the intra-personal space (IPS) in [CITATION_1] .",
